Rating: 3
This is a good weeknight recipe. It's easy to prepare and you can use what you've got in the pantry and freezer. I used chicken breasts on the bone as well as the thighs, and they came out fine. (I worried they would get too dry.) I added some thyme and bay leaf while I was cooking, and a couple of extra cranks of fresh black pepper before serving.

